<div><title>currentColor is mixed with the correct color-space in color-mix()</title></div>
<link rel="help" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-color-5/#color-mix"ó €º>
<link rel="author" href="https://mozilla.org" title="Mozilla">
<style>
div {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background-color: red;
  color: red;
  background-color: color-mix(in lch, currentColor 50%, blue);
}
div div {
  color: green;
  background-color: inherit;
}
</style>
